channel.title: Best low level P2P Money Making?
channel.description: So this is going to sound really noobish, but I am pretty pissed right now... I have never been a member on Runescape but just now decided i need to be. My guy is only a cb lvl 70. I had 10m on it, full zammy. full sara and the regular rune. I had to leave for a week cause i went out of town, when i logged back into my rs account everything was gone..... No zammy, no sara, no 10m and not even the reg rune... :mad: And now, I just don't feel like going through 4 months or more of getting it all back. I know that P2P you can earn money like 10 times as fast, so i want to know what the best P2P way to make money is from level 1 in all P2P levels...

item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

I wish I could find a team to make gps with:(, team work is best money ingame unless you can solo nex ofc.
Even if people are a much lower level than you and you split 50/50 you still can make so much more money being a team than doing lets say frosties 99 range void etc.
